<div id="jQueryInsiderGuide" class="popup-container" style="display: none;">
  <%= form_tag save_guide_setting_path, :id => 'jQueryGuideForm', :remote => true do %>
    <fieldset class="fieldset-border" style="padding:18px 45px 25px 45px;">
      <legend>
        <h2 class="sg-legend-margin">Meet Your Insider!</h2>
      </legend>
      <div class="row-fluid" style="text-align:justify;">
        <p>Your Insider will tirelessly comb the web to bring you relevant offers, suggestions, and activities for you and your family.</p>
        <p>You may now go to those other daily deal sites and unsubscribe to those annoying email blasts – because now, you will get the offers that are relevant to you.</p>
        <p>Insider runs the gamut from suggesting activities for you and your family to do on your days off to tailoring offers that take you away from life’s daily hassles.</p>
        <p>Share offers with trusted friends and maybe you’ll be sharing a relaxing day at a spa for an amazing price!</p>
        <p><strong>*To get the best out of Insider,</strong> spend a moment to update your <strong><%= insider_preferences_link %></strong> so Insider can bring you only the most relevant offers and weed out results you would not be interested in.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span8">
          <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span1">
              <%= check_box_tag 'user_profile[show_insider_guide]', "false" %>
            </div>
            <div class="span6">
              <label for="user_profile_show_insider_guide" style="line-height: 25px;">Don't Show Again</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <%= hidden_field_tag 'guide_page', 'insider' %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </fieldset>
  <% end %>
</div>